    {
      "id": 34,
      "type": "MarkdownNote",
      "pos": [
        2245.1726908021337,
        1472.3980951429082
      ],
      "size": [
        459.7594954553688,
        638.8659915696926
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 2,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "title": "‎",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Higgs_v3-TTS-ComfyUI Model Requirements\n\n**VRAM:** Recommended BF16 usage is roughly **10-12 GB VRAM** during generation depending on text length, voice cloning references, attention backend, and other loaded models.\n\nHiggs v3 has **AIMDO / ComfyUI model-management integration** for unload support and VRAM visualization.\n\n**higgsv3tts** (main TTS model)\n\n- 🤗 [bosonai/higgs-audio-v3-tts-4b — model.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/bosonai/higgs-audio-v3-tts-4b/resolve/main/model.safetensors?download=true)\n\n**audio_encoders** (optional Whisper transcription node)\n\n- 🤗 openai/whisper-large-v3-turbo (recommended)\n- 🤗 openai/whisper-large-v3\n- 🤗 openai/whisper-medium\n- 🤗 openai/whisper-small\n- 🤗 openai/whisper-tiny\n\n## Model Storage Location\n\n```text\nComfyUI/\n└── models/\n    ├── higgsv3tts/\n    │   └── higgs-audio-v3-tts-4b/\n    │       └── model.safetensors\n    └── audio_encoders/\n        ├── openai_whisper-large-v3-turbo/\n        ├── openai_whisper-large-v3/\n        ├── openai_whisper-medium/\n        ├── openai_whisper-small/\n        └── openai_whisper-tiny/\n```\n\n`model.safetensors` may also be placed directly in:\n\n```text\nComfyUI/models/higgsv3tts/model.safetensors\n```\n\nIf `download_if_missing` is enabled, missing assets are downloaded automatically.\n\n## Links\n\n- [Issues](https://github.com/Saganaki22/Higgs_v3-TTS-ComfyUI/issues)\n- [Higgs_v3-TTS-ComfyUI](https://github.com/Saganaki22/Higgs_v3-TTS-ComfyUI)\n- [Official Higgs Audio v3 Model Repository](https://huggingface.co/bosonai/higgs-audio-v3-tts-4b)"
      ],
      "color": "#222",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
